    <note>Wang(2) Dongmei [19221] Su Zhe, WJ, 24.2b-3b (wife, born Su, who married him at age 20 and died in 1101 at age 75). I am assuming, without any documentary evidence, that Dongmei was from the same lineage as Su(1) Shi's [3767] wife, a Meizhou, Qingshen Wang(2), whose great grandfather, Weide [19222], moved from Meishan to Qingshen. Since Dongmei was from the same generation as the Su(1) brothers, I am making him the lineage (third) nephew of Su(1) Shi's father-in-law, Fang(2) [19172] (or Jie).</note>
